    <item>
      <title>英国工党改变免税养老金限额计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/uk-s-labour-party-u-turns-on-plans-for-tax-free-pension-limit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国五大政党本周准备发布各自的竞选宣言，而各方对于如何兑现竞选承诺存在疑问，而英国反对党工党已放弃重新引入养老金储蓄免税限额的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/uk-s-labour-party-u-turns-on-plans-for-tax-free-pension-limit</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 22:46:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利欧盟选举中奥尔班险胜 挑战者数量激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/orban-ekes-out-win-in-hungary-s-eu-vote-as-challenger-surges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利举行的欧洲议会选举中，总理维克托·奥尔班领导的执政党失利，此次选举的一大特点是出现了一位新贵政治家，他准备挑战这位连任五届的领导人的主导地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/orban-ekes-out-win-in-hungary-s-eu-vote-as-challenger-surges</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 21:34:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比利时选举中保守党获胜，阻止极右翼压倒性胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/conservative-win-blocks-far-right-landslide-in-belgium-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比利时选民对首相亚历山大·德克罗的执政联盟表示了谴责，尽管如此，极右翼政党并没有像民意调查所预测的那样获得压倒性胜利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/conservative-win-blocks-far-right-landslide-in-belgium-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 21:32:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普提出免税小费政策以赢得拉斯维加斯工人的支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/trump-floats-tax-free-tips-in-pitch-to-las-vegas-service-workers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普表示，如果他入主白宫，他将取消对酒店服务人员的小费收入征税，这是他在重罪判决后对内华达州摇摆州选民发出的反击信号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/trump-floats-tax-free-tips-in-pitch-to-las-vegas-service-workers</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 20:20:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>极右翼获胜后马克龙宣布举行法国立法选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/macron-calls-french-legislative-elections-after-eu-vote-defeat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日的欧洲议会选举中，法国和德国选民给本国领导人造成了沉重打击，导致埃马纽埃尔·马克龙做出提前举行立法选举的极端决定，这有可能让正准备举办奥运会的国家陷入政治混乱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/macron-calls-french-legislative-elections-after-eu-vote-defeat</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 19:08:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多将于本周就有争议的税收改革进行投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/trudeau-to-call-vote-on-contentious-tax-change-this-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多的政府将于本周就提高资本利得税纳入税率的计划进行投票，此举将为政府带来数十亿美元的额外收入，并引起了加拿大商界的愤怒。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/trudeau-to-call-vote-on-contentious-tax-change-this-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 18:50:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>甘茨因总理未能满足要求而辞去以色列政府职务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/israel-s-gantz-quits-war-cabinet-after-ultimatum-to-netanyahu</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本尼·甘茨辞去以色列紧急政府职务并呼吁举行选举，并批评总理本雅明·内塔尼亚胡对哈马斯战争的处理方式。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/israel-s-gantz-quits-war-cabinet-after-ultimatum-to-netanyahu</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 17:54:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登警告特朗普未参加战争公墓的孤立主义活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/biden-warns-of-isolationism-at-american-cemetery-trump-skipped</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登在参观法国的一座美国军人公墓时警告美国孤立主义的抬头，而他的前任唐纳德·特朗普六年前曾没有前往这座公墓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/biden-warns-of-isolationism-at-american-cemetery-trump-skipped</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 15:51:43 GMT</pubDate>
